Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭從未結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯盟宇宙軍以及拉爾康帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都假設戰爭將會來臨而開始備戰的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續創下歷史性勝利的驅逐艦微風號的乘員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接獲軍司令部之命到地上執勤兼度假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的休憩時間流逝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳，拜託啦，還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，這是我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.95,0:00:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.03,0:01:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個給你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.70,0:01:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.24,0:01:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我母親的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.14,0:01:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會保佑你的 你要珍惜它喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.18,0:01:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.55,0:01:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打開蓋子看看 那是小音樂盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16歲的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕說不要就是不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不吃早餐對身體不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.74,0:02:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，聽說你心情不好 是發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.71,0:02:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微臣不知這個請情是否妥當，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接切入正題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我方與敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星聯盟宇宙軍的和平狀況持續太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊士氣可能衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候更應該加強全體戒備以防備敵人攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.97,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高第國內的危機意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請陛下在殿前會議上發表演說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕認為沒有必要 你又想開始無益的戰爭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，想不到這會是我們神聖拉爾康帝國皇帝講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國應該征服全銀河…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕不想征服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是帝國全民的民意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請皇帝陛下想想自己的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為皇帝的立場嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴哥巴哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是無法達成的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.09,0:04:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆大人求見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆嗎，叫他進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.14,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下，明天屬下將前往比修拉姆星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故前來問候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比修拉姆？你是說你要去比修拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.92,0:04:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…是去休息嗎 你就慢慢享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，屬下是去哪裡做資源調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？不是去保養嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，在那場戰爭之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比修拉姆長期沒有開發 其實那裡是資源的寶庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，去的時候小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比修拉姆還有蝗蟲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特洛每號巡洋艦，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.44,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離旗艦美爾巴號 現在向比修拉姆星前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更改去比修拉姆星的航行路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就必須繞路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.59,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 選擇流星群較少的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有幾年了 這裡還是一樣沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.47,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 你還記得納斯草原吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是陛下以前喜歡的有蝗蟲的草原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，朕常跟魯烏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不跟朕一起去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，比修拉姆星已經跟以前不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊阿修蘭公國雖然已毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在這裡的阿修蘭遺民仍然一心想復國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說連散步都不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶陛下來這地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知該如何向羅那瓦提督報告了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朕強迫你帶我來的 放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.25,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你切莫忘記皇帝的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕就是為了要忘記啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這個太重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是兔子 不，比兔子更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是野豬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點也沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然，魯烏，你還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕是愛薩琳，你忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳!? 這麼說你是拉爾康的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 朕是愛薩琳啊，魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 烏魯王子已經認不出您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是陛下 他誰也認不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯王子，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯王子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然檢回一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.95,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後也不知是不是喪失所有記憶…還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經對所有事物都喪失興趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕曾聽說阿修蘭一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿修蘭大公違抗先皇命令而被滿門抄斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已為你已經死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.81,0:12:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，我是侍女長米蘭達 請陛下大發慈悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過魯烏王子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是以為朕會逮捕魯烏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕在魯烏面前只是普通女孩愛薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.89,0:12:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏無法恢復了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.70,0:12:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到邊境星球之後 病況一直沒有起色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才冒險帶他回來比修拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡本來是阿修蘭的領地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是魯烏的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得帶他回來是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.72,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他接觸往日的回憶 可以稍微打開他的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳，明年夏天你一定會過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的，我一定會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏王子，魯烏王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達 明天也帶魯烏來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心，朕不會害他 朕想讓魯烏看一個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式的，她說人不太舒服 正在休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.89,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，我是多姆，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.95,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏，這個 這是你母親的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，魯烏王子還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.74,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂盒已經不響了 再也無法回到那時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏王子還需要一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.65,0:15:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這是他第一次自己伸手拿東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.59,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，雖然不是很明顯 病況已經漸有起色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達，快點靠岸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏，我們去捉蝗蟲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捉蝗蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，我捉到這麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比修蘭爪黑蝗蟲 只有這個星球才有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳你真了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.12,0:16:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你說這麼多幹什麼 不會是想炸來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要養它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要養它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.07,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.44,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放它們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放它們走吧！為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.84,0:16:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它們關在小籠子裡面太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一步也離不開宮殿妳會怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓它們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳很偉大喔 這樣才是公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，是多姆，別嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕對這裡熟得就像自家花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花園之中有安慰陛下心靈的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有，有，有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分一些給你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆最討厭蝗蟲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕還抓了好多蝗蟲可是全部都逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏對朕是百依百順呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是把陛下當作妹妹看待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣躺著 什麼憂愁都能忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果永遠這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.50,0:18:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對阿修蘭人而言他們希望王子趕快復原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏王子成為下一任皇帝復興阿修蘭公國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們阿修蘭人的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復興阿修蘭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來，不就又得跟拉爾康軍交戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要魯烏與朕對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會那麼希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你們不知道朕跟魯烏的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算魯烏是朕的敵人 朕也無法跟他交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的 魯烏王子成為皇帝以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會為阿修蘭而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟朕敵對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是敵人 哪還分誰是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是阿修蘭公國的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要後天回去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，資源調查結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下必須準備出席殿前會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕不回去 朕還想在這裡待一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.87,0:19:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，你是神聖拉爾康帝國的皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕不是自願要當皇帝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然不會改變可是人會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不能永遠活在回憶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕說不回去就是不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.84,0:20:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達，魯烏真的一定得當皇帝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是魯烏王子的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為像他父王一樣的好皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下沒想過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想，朕從沒那麼想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了，魯烏笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，再給他看那個錶 說不定他會恢復記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏的記憶恢復的話就會成為朕的的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 就算魯烏王子恢復記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為陛下的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.29,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是一樣沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.06,0:21:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時朕得對付他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其真魯烏為敵 還不如趁現在捉住魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你捉吧 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你捉走魯烏王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.55,0:21:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他的記憶一恢復 就會跟拉爾康帝國交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.03,0:21:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我米蘭達不惜豁出性命保護烏魯王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非交戰不可嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.50,0:21:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是皇帝嗎 皇帝就不能為自己而活嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.04,0:21:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，每個人都有非走不可的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.94,0:21:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法為自己而活的不只是皇帝而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.45,0:22:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.97,0:22:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下請為屋子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.07,0:22:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊阿修蘭公國的王子必須逮捕起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.98,0:22:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要捉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.25,0:22:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不然會引起災禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只會危害陛下也會危及帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.36,0:22:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉下來 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.99,0:22:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.99,0:22:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達，把魯烏帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.90,0:22:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.13,0:22:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，請三思吧 事關拉爾康帝國的存亡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭瘩，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.75,0:23:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.85,0:23:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.98,0:23:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上神聖拉爾康帝國威信與朕的名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.35,0:23:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准逮捕他們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯烏!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.09,0:23:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你舉刀向朕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.87,0:24:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕身為皇帝一定接受你的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.05,0:24:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.30,0:24:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.98,0:24:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，你還是休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.54,0:25:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.67,0:25:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的日子會造訪這個宇宙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.58,0:25:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要陛下希望的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.85,0:25:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕是這麼希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.36,0:25:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔 嗯，我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.03,0:25:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開蓋子看看 那是音樂盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.95,0:25:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美的曲子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.05,0:26:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是母親鼓勵我要成為好皇帝，送給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.32,0:26:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著它 你也可以成為好皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.36,0:26:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳成為好皇帝以後再還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.47,0:26:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要成為好皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.74,0:26:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好皇帝嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.61,0:26:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛薩琳你也這麼想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.44,0:26:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我也這麼希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.67,0:26:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.24,0:26:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖蕩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.75,0:27:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼小時候的殘影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.46,0:27:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將心託付給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.77,0:27:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.21,0:27:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.48,0:27:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.58,0:27:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那清澈個眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.85,0:27:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.09,0:27:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.46,0:27:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使時光流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.30,0:27:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到重逢的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.29,0:28:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.67,0:28:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.87,0:28:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.05,0:28:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成為大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.48,0:28:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的這個笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.59,0:28:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請不要讓它有所改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.89,0:28:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.93,0:28:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使分離得再遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.07,0:29:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到重逢的那一天
